Class Contestant

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • clientSide.entities.Contestant
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class Contestant
extends java.lang.Thread
    The Contestant class represents a contestant entity in the game simulation. Contestants participate in various activities during the game and follow instructions from coaches.
